.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, pakistani, malaysian
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, chess, singing
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike
1. the spanish is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the pakistani##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Nationality    | malaysian  | spanish  | pakistani        |
| Hobby       | singing | chess | board-games |
| Transport   | boat    | car   | quad-bike   |

