3. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the japanese is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Nationality     | japanese      | brazilian | argentine |
| Pet     | chinchilla | bird      | rat           |
| Sport   | water-polo | climbing  | volleyball    |

