1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating mango##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person eating mango is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | tea      | sprite     |
| Food         | garlic  | nectarine | mango        |
| Transport   | jet-ski | train    | helicopter |

