2. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of country##1
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta  | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | country  | pop    | disco       |
| Food   | pepper   | pumpkin | blueberry   |

